//TEXT
<jaT0001>Meanwhile, at that time...
<enT0001>Meanwhile, at that time...

//TEXT 【Boy】
<jaT0002>"Hah...."
<enT0002>"Hah...."

//TEXT
<jaT0003>The boy sitting in the sofa yawned, looking too relaxed.
<enT0003>The boy sitting in the sofa yawned, looking too relaxed.

//TEXT 【Boy】
<jaT0004>"I'm bored. Whenever I'm on break, there's never anything to do."
<enT0004>"I'm bored. Whenever I'm on break, there's never anything to do."

//TEXT
<jaT0005>His name was Aizawa Ryota.
<enT0005>His name was Aizawa Ryota.

//TEXT
<jaT0006>He had come to the Aries for training as a prep division cadet of the Central Military Preparatory Academy.
<enT0006>He had come to the Aries for training as a prep division cadet of the Central Military Preparatory Academy.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0007>"I can't believe every day is like this. Damn it, if I'd known it was like this, I would've risked it being confiscated and brought a game or something."
<enT0007>"I can't believe every day is like this. Damn it, if I'd known it was like this, I would've risked it being confiscated and brought a game or something."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0008>"Nobu-chan and Kan-chan... I wonder what they're doing now. It's not fair. Everyone else is off having fun."
<enT0008>"Nobu-chan and Kan-chan... I wonder what they're doing now. It's not fair. Everyone else is off having fun."

//TEXT
<jaT0009>Ryota said with a big sigh. There is a reason he's grumbling here, aside from his habit of talking to himself.
<enT0009>Ryota said with a big sigh. There is a reason he's grumbling here, aside from his habit of talking to himself.

//TEXT
<jaT0010>Central Military Academy held the stance that "one should strive to do things on one's own". Ryota loyally upholded this stance, so he was stuck here alone, dying of boredom.
<enT0010>Central Military Academy held the stance that "one should strive to do things on one's own". Ryota loyally upholded this stance, so he was stuck here alone, dying of boredom.

//TEXT
<jaT0011>Most third year cadets ignore this stance, and close friends take classes with each other.
<enT0011>Most third year cadets ignore this stance, and close friends take classes with each other.

//TEXT
<jaT0012>However, he didn't know this until after the fact so he sits here unnecessarily bored.
<enT0012>However, he didn't know this until after the fact so he sits here unnecessarily bored.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0013>"Aniki said he was coming so maybe I'll wait for him... But he's temperamental. There really isn't any guarantee he'll come."
<enT0013>"Aniki said he was coming so maybe I'll wait for him... But he's temperamental. There really isn't any guarantee he'll come."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0014>"Hah... hah... hah... I want to go home."
<enT0014>"Hah... hah... hah... I want to go home."

//TEXT
<jaT0015>This is but one of the many times Ryota has said this today.
<enT0015>This is but one of the many times Ryota has said this today.

//TEXT
<jaT0016>He was not completely without hope though.
<enT0016>He was not completely without hope though.

